 ♫ Autumn winds sigh ♫ 

518
00:42:51,760 --> 00:42:53,680
 ♫ Moon and stars dapple the sky ♫ 

519
00:42:53,680 --> 00:42:57,720
 ♫ Brushing the loneliness of bygone days ♫ 

