00:43:07,760 --> 00:43:09,720
 ♫ The color of light ♫ 

525
00:43:09,720 --> 00:43:13,720
 ♫ To warm your frozen soul ♫ 

526
00:43:13,720 --> 00:43:15,560
 ♫ Memories anchor here ♫ 

