00:43:29,760 --> 00:43:31,640
 ♫ Burning away ♫ 

533
00:43:31,640 --> 00:43:37,720
 ♫ All these karmic ties ♫ 

534
00:43:37,720 --> 00:43:39,920
 ♫ To save you ♫ 

535
00:43:39,920 --> 00:43:41,960
 ♫ To save me ♫ 

536
00:43:41,960 --> 00:43:45,840
 ♫ To cross over all suffering,
I'll break through ♫ 

537
00:43:45,840 --> 00:43:48,080
 ♫ The laws of heaven ♫ 

538
00:43:48,080 --> 00:43:49,880
 ♫ The vortex of reincarnation ♫ 

539
00:43:49,880 --> 00:43:54,040
 ♫ What of life and death? ♫ 

